text:
Hey Folks, 

I'm a freelance writer, and I would be launching a course this month talking about how to land high-paying clients as a freelance writer. I am looking to collaborate with an SEO copywriter to be on my course.

Benefit - You'd get 10% of my total sales for the next three months from the date the course is launched.

Send an email to <mailto:lanisodunke@gmail.com|lanisodunke@gmail.com> to learn more if you're interested in collaborating. 

Thanks!
